      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BRAZEN SAILOR (2) has been racing in consistent fashion and went close to winning when finishing a game second over 1200m at this track 3 weeks ago. He maps to receive the run of the race early on, and he looks like the one they will all have to beat. CAPISTAN (3) worked hard after pressing forward from a wide draw before sticking on gamely for third over 1600m here. He is well placed to figure in the top 3 again. KING BLING (4) was safely held last time out but is better than that performance suggests and he should be close to his peak fitness now. Stick with him for all top 4 combos. HIGHLANDS (1) returned to form with a solid third at this venue and is expected to take further improvement from that effort. From the inside draw, he has definite each-way claims. SPLISH SPLASH (5) showed encouraging improvement last start and the step up in distance should suit her. Include in all top 4 combos to be safe.",
